    "All three studies (A11, A13, and A28) have mentioned the key roles of governance in healthcare AI.",
    "Notably, no study among these 6 has focused on industry-level governance.",
    "As discussed earlier, the classification of stakeholders under different levels i.e., team, organization, industry, national and international has been done based on the study by Lu et al. [1].AI governance varies significantly across regions, reflecting distinct geopolitical priorities.",
